{{ja-kanjitab|こうべ|yomi=k}}

{{IPAchar|/kamipe/}} → {{IPAchar|/kampe/}} → {{IPAchar|/kaube/}} → {{IPAchar|/kɔːbe/}} → {{IPAchar|/koːbe/}}

Compound of either {{m|ja|上|tr=kami||upper}} or {{m|ja|髪|tr=kami||hair}} (likely [[cognate]]s) with the suffix {{m|ja|方|tr=pe||location, direction}}.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref><ref name="DJR">{{R:Daijirin}}</ref><ref name="DJS">{{R:Daijisen}}</ref>

Alternatively, may be an alteration from {{lang|ja|頭}} (''kabu'', “head”, see above) + {{m|ja|上|tr=ue||up}}.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref>

